      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUNSET AGRIPPINA (2) looks close to another win after hitting the frame in a 2.5 lengths second (22.84) in a Grade 5/6 at this track. Got the money at her only try from this box. Can go on with it. ELITE CRACKER (5) is rarely far away but tends to find one better, placing 14 from 24 starts. Finished third (22.86) at this track last time making it four minors on end. Well placed and gets his chance. FORMULA FIRE (4) turned in a plain effort last time when seventh at this track over 400m behind Monkey Magic (23.51) in a Grade 5/6. Can figure in the finish. MOO MOVE (7) is a last start winner who can measure up again.",
